	<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Excellent Team for Rubber Material Technology</strong></span></p>
<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">We understand that even the best-designed part in the world can still fail if it's not made of the right material. That's why we pay close attention to application variables and help our customers choose the best material for each situation. If need be, we can formulate and test custom compounds in our very own material development laboratories. Our material labs focus on mixing and milling, curing and aging, and physical testing of finished compounds. Taken together, those endeavors allow us to achieve just the right blend of properties before a single part is molded.</span></p>
<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The end result of our efforts? Our expertise in material development ultimately results in useful, effective compounds, and, by extension, product reliability. Best of all, that reliability, by further extension, results in even greater peace of mind for our customers, who can rely on our products to perform in the field as expected.</span></p> 
			
				
